title: 33 Immortals: Try Out New Features in the Fourth Playtest from May 20
description: 33 Immortals is back for Xbox Insiders with a fourth playtest starting Tuesday, May 20, 8am PT (11am ET). The playtest will be available for 6 days and end on Monday, May 26, 8am PT (11am ET).
